Neighbors

title: Cats
text:
Cats are fascinating creatures. They are related to big cats like lions and tigers.
Cats are often compared to dogs as popular pets.

title: Parrots
text:
Parrots are colorful and intelligent birds. Unlike penguins, parrots can fly.
Some parrot species can live as long as dogs or cats.
